data.description: Under Construction. VALENCIA DEL SOL-newest Active 55+ Gated Resort Community in southern Hillsborough.  COME LIVE THE LIFESTYLE!!!  BUILDERS INCENTIVE OF $20,000 is reflected in the Sales Price.  The 2,000+ sq.ft. 2 bdrms. 2-1/2 baths YORK VILLA has a nice sized master bedroom with two large walk-in closets and dual sinks in the bath.  The covered entry opens to the foyer and formal dining room across from the kitchen/great room combo.  The beautiful gourmet kitchen with granite counter tops offers stainless steel GE appliances including side by side refrigerator, free standing gas stove for all you chefs, microwave vented to the outside with lights above and below the upgraded cabinets.  In the front of the home is an en suite for guests or could serve as a 2nd master.  The den or 3rd bedroom is spacious for a bedroom, office or study.  A large storage near the foyer is across from separate laundry with a GE Electric washer and gas dryer, built-in cabinet under sink and cabinets above.   The great room opens to a screen, enclosed lanai to sit peacefully and watch the water.  The HOA fees include: pressure washing exterior, pest control, termite treatment and exterior repainting.  The future brings a planned 25,000 s.f. clubhouse with social hall; raised stage/dance floor; restaurant-indoor/outdoor seating; card room; fitness center; exercise studio; massage room; resort style pool; spa; pickle ball; tennis; bocce ball, small and large dog park.  There is something for everyone and a VISIT to VALENCIA DEL SOL is a MUST!!
